acceptance_criteria: "Public SDK mutation inputs are typed per-action (derived from flag/schema contracts, not hand-written) so field typos and wrong value types fail tsc under strict; projected list rows expose typed id/core fields; no runtime behavior change; typed surface covered by a type-level test (tsd or equivalent)"
